branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The VX2 for steam (up to 183 &#xb0;C) is available with brass and stainless steel body. Three body sizes are available, with port size ranges from 1/8 to 1/2 inch. High temperature FKM seal and Class H coil insulation are standard. Flow rate ranges from Cv of 0.23 to 2.21.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchCategory.bullets:
&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;IP65 enclosure
&lt;LI&gt; Normally Closed and Normally Open type available, Class H coil
&lt;LI&gt;Special construction improves service life when compared with current shading coil
&lt;LI&gt;Power consumption: size 1 – 9 w; size 2 – 12 w; size 3 - 15w
&lt;LI&gt;Body material: brass (C37), stainless steel&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Can be used with heated water&#xa0;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;

